dct_alternative_sm: Official map of Michigan : railroad, township and sectional / compiled under the direction of the Commissioner of Railroads.
dct_description_sm: Includes table showing counties and county seats; population of counties, census of 1884; miles of railroads in each county, Jan 1, 1885; location of state institutions.
Includes list of state lands subject to purchase at the State Land Office., Mich., May 1, 1885.
